Steps installing Laravel:
Download XAMPP
Download Cmder
Download node js
Download composer php manager & install through setup.exe
install laravel through these commands:
composer global require laravel/installer
laravel new example-app


install Bootstap in laravel:
composer require laravel/ui
php artisan ui bootstrap
npm install
npm run dev
npm run dev   (again)


Instal SASS:
npm install -g sass
install Live Sass Compiler
click on watch SASS from bottom right


install Less:
npm install -g less
npm i less --save-dev
lessc public/css/site.less > public/css/site.css 


Important Commands:
php artisan make:controller FormController
php artisan make:migration add_images_url_to_products_table --table=products   ->   (Add column to table)
php artisan make:model Products -m   ->   (create model & table)
